You got any concept
about personal property?

342
00:18:27,928 --> 00:18:31,223
You know, like how about
personal private moments

343
00:18:31,383 --> 00:18:34,400
in the privacy of one's
personal, private space?

344
00:18:34,856 --> 00:18:36,528
Do you understand what I'm saying?

345
00:18:36,800 --> 00:18:38,742
- I know what privacy means.
- I understand

346
00:18:38,902 --> 00:18:40,976
that you're my wife's sister
but we've been wondering

347
00:18:41,136 --> 00:18:43,658
when is it, exactly, that you're
gonna get a place of your own?

348
00:18:47,923 --> 00:18:49,653
I didn't mean it to come out like that.

349
00:18:49,813 --> 00:18:51,521
- Oh, my God.
- That came out wrong.

350
00:18:52,260 --> 00:18:53,836
That came out wrong.
I'm sorry.

351
00:18:54,096 --> 00:18:55,129
Just stop talking.

352
00:18:55,735 --> 00:18:57,885
- I didn't mean to say it like that.
- No, I heard you,

353
00:18:58,045 --> 00:18:59,886
it's fine. I'll take the laundry.

354
00:19:00,046 --> 00:19:01,885
I just feel kind of stupid right now.

355
00:19:02,845 --> 00:19:03,845
It's fine.

356
00:19:14,251 --> 00:19:15,482
Come on in.

357
00:19:16,595 --> 00:19:18,039
Oh, she's with me, Coach.

358
00:19:18,766 --> 00:19:19,903
Noelle.

359
00:19:20,163 --> 00:19:22,197
Yes, hi.
