362
00:19:28,505 --> 00:19:31,582
- I think I've ever seen.
- I'm glad you noticed. Thank you.

363
00:19:31,842 --> 00:19:33,292
You're welcome.

364
00:19:33,552 --> 00:19:35,547
So imagine your phone is
ringing off the hook.

365
00:19:35,707 --> 00:19:37,871
