368
00:19:43,436 --> 00:19:44,436
Alabama?

369
00:19:44,935 --> 00:19:46,129
Anything else?

370
00:19:46,289 --> 00:19:48,298
Lots of places, Coach.
We're thinking

371
00:19:48,458 --> 00:19:50,559
