would be beneficial.

372
00:19:50,819 --> 00:19:52,834
It's lots of coverage, good exposure.

373
00:19:52,994 --> 00:19:54,622
So I roll on over to Alabama.

374
00:19:54,782 --> 00:19:58,025
Coach has got good ties to the pros,
and I'm living the NFL dream.

375
00:19:59,471 --> 00:20:00,277
TMU?

376
00:20:00,986 --> 00:20:02,571
