00:20:02,831 --> 00:20:04,843
They're getting back
at you for walkin' on 'em.

378
00:20:05,003 --> 00:20:07,413
Any history between me and TMU
has nothing to do with you.

379
00:20:07,573 --> 00:20:09,477
They want you,
they're gonna come after you.

380
00:20:09,637 --> 00:20:12,247
Look, the point is
I gotta make a verbal, Coach.

381
00:20:12,762 --> 00:20:15,125
Before you hear from TMU,
you gotta make your verbal?

382
00:20:15,502 --> 00:20:16,502
I mean...

383
00:20:17,301 --> 00:20:18,962
What am I supposed to do?

384
00:20:19,535 --> 00:20:22,049
All right, let me tell you what I know
about Alabama, then.

385
00:20:22,602 --> 00:20:25,839
They got the best running back
in the conference: Demetrius Walsh.

386
00:20:25,999 --> 00:20:28,132
And another thing:
he is not going pro either...

387
00:20:28,292 --> 00:20:30,807
- He's staying his senior year, we know.
- That's one year.

388
00:20:32,001 --> 00:20:34,144
I can handle it if it means Alabama.

389
00:20:34,404 --> 00:20:38,065
What about Waters? 500 yards this year.
He's a freshman backup.

390
00:20:38,571 --> 00:20:42,069
He's already mastered their offense,
which is extremely complicated.

391
00:20:42,329 --> 00:20:45,056
Now, that's your sophomore, junior year
