schools that need you to play now.

395
00:20:55,129 --> 00:20:56,617
It's gonna be a fight.

396
00:20:56,777 --> 00:20:58,836
You gotta give yourself
the opportunity to play,

397
00:20:59,096 --> 00:21:00,504
the opportunity to be seen.

398
00:21:00,764 --> 00:21:03,105
