settle down, take a breath.

399
00:21:03,265 --> 00:21:06,385
And you definitely want
to look at the fine print, son.

400
00:21:07,028 --> 00:21:09,778
I'm saying: be patient.
Don't let 'em pressure you.

401
00:21:11,341 --> 00:21:13,934
And don't end up making any
emotional decisions.

402
00:21:15,036 --> 00:21:16,520
That makes a lot of sense.

403
00:21:18,568 --> 00:21:20,127
What does your mother say?

404
00:21:20,395 --> 00:21:21,441
My mom?

405
00:21:21,701 --> 00:21:24,298
