412
00:21:41,158 --> 00:21:42,546
Now get the hell out of here.

413
00:21:42,806 --> 00:21:45,340
- Let me finish my lunch.
- Appreciate it.

414
00:21:45,854 --> 00:21:48,663
- Let me know you need anything else.
- All right.

415
00:22:01,491 --> 00:22:04,336
- What are you doing?
