417
00:22:08,484 --> 00:22:11,116
Well, hon, he's in a terrible...
He's such a grump this week.

418
00:22:11,767 --> 00:22:14,620
No, he didn't mean it.
Come on, let's go back in the house...

419
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:17,456
- Sweetie, come on now.
