438
00:24:05,407 --> 00:24:06,523
No, I didn't.

439
00:24:06,783 --> 00:24:07,908
What happened?

440
00:24:08,068 --> 00:24:10,151
I asked your sister
when she was gonna leave.

441
00:24:10,698 --> 00:24:14,388
