and she pretty much inferred the rest.

442
00:24:14,548 --> 00:24:16,533
And that's pretty much what happened.

443
00:24:17,064 --> 00:24:20,417
I wish maybe you'd talked to me
before you'd had that conversation.

444
00:24:21,078 --> 00:24:22,078
OK.

445
00:24:23,935 --> 00:24:26,107
And in the future, if there's
a family member of mine

446
00:24:26,267 --> 00:24:27,986
that's gonna be kicked out
of this house,

447
00:24:28,146 --> 00:24:30,087
I would prefer that I do
the kicking out.

448
00:24:31,753 --> 00:24:32,756
OK.

449
00:24:34,892 --> 00:24:35,892
OK.

450
00:24:40,818 --> 00:24:44,424
