452
00:24:47,750 --> 00:24:49,180
So now I'm broke,

453
00:24:50,185 --> 00:24:53,480
And Jackie's going crazy
'cause she's got a kid,

454
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:56,095
and I got no money to pay for the house.

455
00:24:56,711 --> 00:24:59,756
And, you know, that's when
she bailed on me.

456
00:25:03,298 --> 00:25:05,763
I don't know what else
there is to say about that.

